{"tid":1501601,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"九龍灣 牛頭角 觀塘 逃生路線","createTime":"2019-08-24T11:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T12:18:17.000Z","uid":74100,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"94d04c4759fcbb10b20e31e20fb6cf23e1181035","tid":1501601,"uid":74100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"希望比少少方向大家 有錯唔好屌<br />\n<br />\n如果你現時位於九龍灣淘大 首先去爭鮮 過對面馬路 <br />\n- 入面有架小巴可以去觀塘瑞和街街市<br />\n- 牛頭角街市隔離係安基苑 入面有個商場<br />\n<br />\n1. 你可以搭車落觀塘 去到瑞和街街市 行去和樂邨會有巴士站出旺角13D 尖沙嘴1A 沙田89D 等等<br />\n<br />\n2. 你可以沿安基苑行馬路旁行上樂雅苑 （記住入樂雅苑 如果行出面行前少少係狗屋）入面有條路去樂華村 樂華村入面樂華南村停車場旁邊係林景閣 佢地形係圓形 兩邊都可以出番馬路 沿途可以落功樂道 呢個時候 你可能會遇到以下兩個建築物<br />\n<br />\n- 你會見到觀塘功樂中學 過對面有個球場穿過去就係雲漢村 雲漢村漢柏樓開始有分岔路 <br />\n<br />\n左邊落去係車房 落到盡頭係祥和苑 過對面和樂村 出面可以搭1A 旺角尖沙嘴 13D 旺角 89 89X 89D 大圍 沙田 11X紅磡 601 過海 金鐘 銅鑼灣 <br />\n<br />\n直行落街市 出番市中心<br />\n<br />\n- 你會見到寧波公學 行前少少 有條斜路行落去 沿路係車房 行到天主教小學轉右 第一架小巴去荃灣 葵芳 第二架去西貢彩虹<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果你係九龍灣爭鮮過去牛頭角下村 牛頭角街市出面可以截觀塘小巴 <br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁多 安全路線"},{"pid":"3b4e3dffc746e179306907f17b35f66b704f5a10","tid":1501601,"uid":74100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:53:48.000Z","msg":"歡迎補充"},{"pid":"764835dd5c2de69cf750aed6634414eb97a51fe9","tid":1501601,"uid":110589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"九龍灣成條路塞死"},{"pid":"556436f51de312ce6e0f0000909a4c6ac8751f4c","tid":1501601,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日核彈</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[時事台重開]【是日核彈】【斷正】監控燈柱解剖 直通大陸 證據確鑿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1501550/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1501550/page/1</a><br />\n【資料直通大陸】三思智慧路燈系統有幾恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1501518/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1501518/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudflare-ipfs.com/ipfs/QmRjjkJjYroKDJntMSGkn6aQpFdvJ7Et7DpunaB6wREyhb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudflare-ipfs.com%2Fipfs%2FQmRjjkJjYroKDJntMSGkn6aQpFdvJ7Et7DpunaB6wREyhb&h=831aaccd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99514d5c8071855341bff5e7b2cf3f3cb03cee6d","tid":1501601,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bf9cc8f5efa334778b2c8c24bfe3f47995e57a45","tid":1501601,"uid":74100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"push 希望大家補充"},{"pid":"87267ea622ec453a9276a430fbb56e167c198910","tid":1501601,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e19b74abb80bdcd25af1d6560b8aabd55671746","tid":1501601,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:57:26.000Z","msg":"一句講哂，都係唔明嘅，入淘大。"},{"pid":"dd8d3cca889ddc95938b703c4a3233f73474d6e3","tid":1501601,"uid":134134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e19b74abb80bdcd25af1d6560b8aabd55671746","tid":1501601,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:57:26.000Z","msg":"一句講哂，都係唔明嘅，入淘大。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"同德寶有教會，德寶即係迷你倉三級火嗰度"},{"pid":"2f2e311f8a8aaa45d218d3d1543e86b37ea88f18","tid":1501601,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/9556792778_15ac6ce94c_z.jpg?itok=fF5_DBBU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F9556792778_15ac6ce94c_z.jpg%3Fitok%3DfF5_DBBU&h=afd00ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c2/Hkerfirstagainchiuunion.JPG/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/233?cb=20141216062518\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F